public class LazyTab
extends AbstractTab
implements EventListener<PatientChangedEventArg>

Useful for decorating a AbstractTab. Creates every time a new instance of the containing Tab when it gets displayed. (Within the TabPane of Pivot, always the same instance would be used)

TeamB
